a": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "DESANTIS: This is absurd.  Once a ballot is received in Florida it is immediately logged as received.  Once the election ends at 7pm on election night, we know how many ballots have been cast. Once you know the total number of ballots it closes off avenues for cheating.", "last_comment_created": 1780766212604, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 307, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 0, "created": 1780672675000, "id": "2062916835029475574", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1896040561263640576/bh4Ns8ST_normal.jpg", "displayName": "SCRIBEMOON", "username": "SCRIBEMOON"}, "content": "@RonDeSantis I dropped my ballot on May 13 in a West LA drop box. Tracked it. Got confirmation of receipt on May 15th. It STILL HAS NOT BEEN COUNTED.\nThe official LA registrar spin to the local news is that these \"are all late/day of ballots.\" THIS IS A LIE!", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 5171}, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 788, "created": 1780674058000, "id": "2062922635495751993", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1661519593087676416/z4A1A3gs_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Ron DeSantis", "username": "RonDeSantis"}, "content": "This is absurd.  Once a ballot is received in Florida it is immediately logged as received.  Once the election ends at 7pm on election night, we know how many ballots have been cast. Once you know the total number of ballots it closes off avenues for cheating.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 40794}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_